<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>e-COMMERCE Registration page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="registration.css">
</head>
<style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@200;300;500;600;700;800&display=swap');

* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
}

.container {
    height: 100vh;
    width: 100vw;
    /* background: red; */
    display: flex;
    color: white;
}

.sec1 {
    width: 50%;
   
    background-image:
        linear-gradient(45deg,
            rgba(245, 147, 66, 0.75),
            rgba(8, 83, 156, 0.75)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1698778573517-73bdc44638da?w=500&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHx0b3BpYy1mZWVkfDQ2fDZzTVZqVExTa2VRfHxlbnwwfHx8fHw%3D');
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
    background-color: aqua;
    height: 100%
}

.sec2 {
    width: 50%;
 
    height: 100%
}

.box1 {
    /* background-color: red; */
    height: 70%;
    width: 70%;
    margin: 200px auto 0 auto;
}


.logo h1 {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
    margin-top: 10px;
}

.greeting span {
    color: purple;
}

.text {
    margin-top: 15px;
    font-size: 15px;
}

.policy {
    display: flex;
    margin-top: 50px;
}

.policy a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: white;
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-right: 20px;
}

.box2 {
    height: 70%;
    width: 60%;
    margin: 150px auto 0 auto;
}

.box2 input {
    width: 100%;
    margin: 20px 0;
    height: 30px;
    border: none;
    outline: none;
    font-size: 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid gray;
    color: rgb(2, 2, 58);
  
}

.box2 p,
a {
    margin-top: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: navy;
    font-size: small;
}

.box2 .loginbtn {
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 20px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background-color: rgb(255, 193, 59);
    color: white;
    height: 40px;
    border: none;
    font-size: 20px;
}

.box2 div {
    margin-top: 40px;
}

.box2 div button {
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background-color: white;
    border: 2px solid rgb(255, 193, 59);
    color: rgb(255, 193, 59);
    height: 40px;

    font-size: 20px;
}

button a{
    text-decoration: none;
    color: rgb(255, 193, 59);;
    font-size: 20px;
}

</style>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="sec1">
            <div class="box1">
                <div class="logo">
                    <h1>BuyBest</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="greeting">
                    <h1><span>Hi!</span> Register to your account.</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    <p>Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Est tenetur asperiores itaque, vel
                        totam fuga inventore, repellat unde recusandae at earum eaque iusto voluptas aspernatur odio
                        dicta assumenda in quisquam. Perferendis minima rerum deleniti.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="policy">
                    <p><a href="">Privacypolicy</a></p>
                    <p><a href="">Terms of use</a></p>
                    <p><a href="">Legal Service</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sec2">
            <div class="box2">
                <form action="/register" method="post">
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Full Name.." name="fullName"><br>
                    <input type="email" placeholder="Email.." name="email">
                    <input type="password" placeholder="Password.." name="password">
                    <input type="password" placeholder="Re-enter password.." name="reEnterPassword">
                    
                    
                    <button class="loginbtn">Register</button>
                </form>
                <div>
                    <p>Have an account?</p>
                    <button><a href="/login">Login</a></button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>